data.title: 2011 Prosperita Open
data.meta_description: The 2011 Prosperita Open was a professional tennis tournament played on clay courts. It was the eighth edition of the tournament which was part of the 2011 ATP Challenger Tour. It took place in Ostrava, Czech Republic between April 25 – May 1, 2011.
